high_descs: Turn to the right and face the open box.
Pick the box up from the cabinet.
Go left and then left again to face the lamp in the corner.

high_descs: Turn right to face the brown shelf.

high_descs: Turn right facing the empty box on the red table
Pick up the empty box on top of the table
Carry the box to the corner of the room where the floor lamp is
anns.task_desc: Carry a box while turning on a lamp
